data.description: This beautiful, well-maintained home is ready for its new owners. Nestled in a desirable, well-established neighborhood, this charming two-story home offers the perfect blend of modern convenience and classic charm. The front yard, with its superb landscaping, just kicks up the curb appeal a notch. Equipped with solar panels, the eco-friendly features of this home make it as efficient as it is inviting. Upon entering, you will fall in love with the home's layout. Enjoy the windows that look out over the pool and flood the room with natural light. The downstairs area features two large living spaces, a lovely, updated kitchen with granite counters and bar seating, a dining area, and a guest bath. Heading up the stairs, you will find a spacious owner's suite, two additional guest rooms, two baths, and a laundry area. This home has plenty of built-in storage closets and cabinets. Upon entering the backyard, the pool was resurfaced roughly four years ago and is waiting for some summertime fun. You will enjoy the covered patio and use of the side yard garden area as well. While outside, you can savor family and friend gatherings in the well-designed backyard, complete with a beautiful pool that enhances the property's allure. Don't miss your chance to see this beautiful home; contact your favorite realtor today for a private showing!
